{"tid":1897523,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"想清算黑警就入黎！","createTime":"2020-02-25T18:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T23:11:16.000Z","uid":236646,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d33105f8ec37db9d1fbe189522b10a52c987be96","tid":1897523,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:52:38.000Z","msg":"我地有二百萬人，立會肯投票，肯去做選民<br />\n肯大家一齊七人成團組織工會拎功能組別票<br />\n我地可以有能力影響到特首人選立會否決權<br />\n我地係絕對有能力有條件靠團結去幫死左班手足報仇<br />\n要黑警還眼！我希望報仇唔係口號<br />\n大家諗下幾多手足比人拉晒，仲坐緊監，幾多手足死左比人掉洛街，仲未討回公道！依家大家可以無成本咁去幫手足討回公道，我好希望大家無忘記到721 831 101 同埋一班死左ga手足<br />\n我地一人行多一步，七起七人成團組工會，一齊登記做選民，立法會同埋將來特首選舉成為有影響力ga一分子！！！<br />\n我地一定要手持更多牌先可以將黑警驅逐！"},{"pid":"14f97668dc6509acf76d743e284fd88a195d2ddd","tid":1897523,"uid":79893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:54:26.000Z","msg":"組織工會<br />\n加入公會<br />\n宣揚開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947ef1bf8a175f9814de93ec31c8b0d0778c8f93","tid":1897523,"uid":79893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>組織工會<br />\n加入工會<br />\n宣揚開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b89f2a5762b9071e430285cc32aca619fdf0686e","tid":1897523,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06552ecc0b1d40e66dfe917c204acbe801e1f411","tid":1897523,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T18:57:40.000Z","msg":"登記左做選民實無死"},{"pid":"27f39b6277c054101c2e3874ffb93514cd8463f2","tid":1897523,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T20:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1963cc352452bda66b25